BAGHDAD , December 20 -LRB- Xinhua -RRB- -- The Iraqi Intelligence Department has uncovered a spying ring working for the U.S. Central Intelligence Agency -LRB- CIA -RRB- , Baghdad Television reported today .
The television said that the U.S. agents had fully confessed their activities against Iraq .
Iraqi News Agency said that television stations of Baghdad and Ash - Shabab -LRB- youth -RRB- , which are run by Iraqi President Saddam Hussein 's eldest son Udai , will show the confessions at 22 : 00 local time -LRB- 1900GMT -RRB- .
Iraq has previously accused the CIA agents of working in the northern Kurdish autonomous region against the Iraqi government .
